Global Release 15 DEC 2020
Buy it now at www.dirtydozenmovie.com 
Produced by @badbillymedia 
Directed by @amandawest_nomad 
Available on iTunes, Amazon Prime, AppleTV, XBox, Playstation, Vimeo on Demand, GooglePlay and DVD.
